summary: AN ORDINANCE granting the Fremont Dock Co. permission to use and occupy a portion of Fremont Avenue North under the Fremont Bridge North Approach lying north of the Lake Washington Ship Canal and south of the former Burlington Northern Main Line Right-of-Way, for a ten (10) year term, renewable for two successive ten-year terms, specifying the conditions under which this permit is granted, and providing for acceptance of the permit and conditions.
